This is AWESOME. the only thing i did differently was to use boneless, skinless thighs cut into small pieces. it reduced the cooking time and i don't like bones and skin. otherwise, wouldn't change a thing.

Rating: 3
A very simple and easy dish to make! What I do to faciliate the process however, is to bake the chicken in the oven for about 15-20 minutes @ 250 degrees while I prepare the other ingredients and then, when they are ready, I take the chicken out of the oven and put them into the pot. This cuts down the overall cooking time quite dramatically for me. Cheers & Happy Eating!

